answersResultList.title: Back off a little.
answersResultList.resultContent: Listen: it's over or it's just not gonna happen. You already know this, deep down, when a relationship ends or never has a chance. You have a life, but you might want to add a new hobby if someone is occupying too much of your mental space. Find someone to love who'll love you back. That will be easier if you dial down the intensity and stop talking about the one who got away.
